<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Awesome Website</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f0f4f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #4b6cb7;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #f45b69;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #d94c59;
        }
        main {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #4b6cb7;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My Awesome Website</h1>
        <p>Hosted live on Netlify with GitHub</p>
        <a href="#main" class="btn">Explore</a>
    </header>

    <main id="main">
        <h2>About This Site</h2>
        <p>This is a simple website created using HTML and CSS. You can customize it and deploy instantly with Netlify!</p>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 My Awesome Website</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
